Ingredients for the beauty and skin care soup:
The benefits of White Fungus (Tremella fuciformis): It has a sweet taste and a neutral nature, and it affects the lung, stomach, and kidney meridians. Its effects include strengthening the body, nourishing the kidneys, moistening the intestines, benefiting the stomach, replenishing qi, harmonizing the blood, strengthening the heart, nourishing yin, moistening the lungs, promoting the production of body fluids, enhancing physical vitality, improving brain function, boosting energy, beautifying the skin, making the skin more delicate, and prolonging life. It is used to treat conditions such as cough
The effects of peach gum: It has a bitter taste and a neutral nature, and it is associated with the large intestine and bladder meridians.
Benefits: It promotes blood circulation, helps with urinary disorders, stops diarrhea, relieves pain, and also provides hydration while soothing the intestines. For those who suffer from constipation, consuming more peach gum can be beneficial.
The effects of Goji berries: They have a neutral nature and a sweet taste, and they are associated with the liver and stomach meridians.
Benefits the liver and improves eyesight; nourishes the liver and kidneys; promotes skin whitening and beautification; replenishes body fluids and delays aging.
The benefits of red dates: They have a sweet taste and a mild nature, and they affect the spleen and stomach meridians. Red dates help to strengthen the spleen and stomach, replenish qi, generate body fluids, nourish the blood, and calm the mind. Those with weak spleen and stomach function, insufficient qi and blood, or who suffer from insomnia can benefit from consuming more red dates.
The benefits of longan pulp: It has a sweet taste and a warm nature, and it affects the heart and spleen meridians. It is suitable for those with deficiencies in both the heart and spleen.
Longan pulp can also moisturize the skin and enhance its beauty, nourish the blood and soothe the mind, strengthen the heart and spleen, and boost vitality. It is suitable for people with anemia as well as those who suffer from insomnia.
The effects of lotus seeds: They have a sweet and astringent taste, and a neutral nature. They are associated with the heart, spleen, and kidney meridians.
It helps to soothe the mind and calm the nerves, alleviates symptoms such as palpitations and insomnia, addresses stomach weakness and forgetfulness, relieves irritability and thirst, provides nourishment to replenish deficiencies in the body, and stops excessive urination and seminal emission.
Therefore, this beauty-enhancing soup is not only a delicious dessert but also beneficial for your health!
Eating more can help you feel mentally peaceful and well-balanced!
And it won’t be as expensive as bird’s nest either; eating more of it won’t empty your wallet!
