Thank you very much for choosing our product. Before using our chip, please take 5 minutes to carefully read the following information:
After opening the box, please check whether all the items are present.
If there are any missing items, please contact customer service as soon as possible.
The cover plate on the microfluidic chip is made of PC material; please do not use solvents that can react chemically with PC.
Do not use a syringe to inject the sample directly onto the chip, as this can easily lead to liquid leakage.
Microfluidic chips with ordinary substrates are tested using pure water at an injection pressure of 500 mbar (for channel depths of 100 μm) or 300 mbar (for channel depths of 50 μm) before being shipped.
The chips with glass substrates are tested with pure water at an injection pressure of 800 mbar (for 100 um channels) before shipment. Please be careful not to collide the chips with sharp objects during use, as this may damage the substrate.
During use, please take into account the viscosity of the solution and do not exceed the specified range; otherwise, it may lead to leakage.
For microfluidic microchips with a common substrate, when using a syringe pump for sample injection with pure water, we recommend setting the flow rate below 150 ul/min. For the oil phase, we suggest setting the flow rate below 50 ul/min.
Consider the actual viscosity of the liquid being injected, and gradually increase the value of your flow rate parameter from low to high.
After completing the experiments with the general-purpose chip, make sure to clean the internal channels promptly; otherwise, they may become clogged easily.
Microfluidic chips are considered consumables and cannot be reused repeatedly for an extended period of time.
No refunds or exchanges will be provided if the chip is damaged due to long-term use or improper handling.
If you need a microfluidic chip that can withstand higher pressures or flow rates, please contact customer service to request a custom design.
The normal delivery cycle for the chips is within 1 week. For items in stock, shipping can be arranged within 24 hours after the purchase is confirmed. Please consult with customer service before placing an order.
If you have any questions about how to connect our chip with the sampling system, you can refer to the following link: https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60474873, or search for the WeChat official account “Jiemguo Shengke” for more assistance.
You can also visit our official website (http://www.mesobiosys.com) to download brochures and learn about all our products.
For more information about our company's products, please contact our online customer service.
