The surroundings are really not that great; there are very few restaurants and hardware stores in the area, and the quality of the food at the restaurants is just average.
This elevator is also absolutely frustrating—just like someone suffering from a serious illness, it keeps moving back and forth between -2 and -1. No matter how many times I press the button for my floor, it takes me down the emergency exit to the first floor, only to lead me directly to a furniture store that’s closed. And then I can’t get out through the emergency exit either!
Jiayouzhijia still needs improvement; there are many areas that have not been developed yet.
Address: No. 555, North High-Speed Railway Road 1, Shayibake District. The location is conveniently accessible, with a large parking lot that is even free during the day.
